OL,5, The process of hiring BBC chairman     
OL,6, Richard Sharp is to be reviewed by the 
OL,7, Commissioner of Public Appointments    
OL,8, William Shawcross.                     
OL,10,FIt follows claims Mr Sharp helped      
OL,11,Fsecure a loan of up to #800,000 for the
OL,12,Fthen-prime minister Boris Johnson      
OL,13,Fshortly before getting the BBC job.    
OL,15,FMr Shawcross said his review would     
OL,16,Fensure the process had been "run in    
OL,17,Fcompliance" with government rules.     
OL,19,FMr Sharp said he "simply connected"    
OL,20,Fpeople and did not arrange financing.  
